    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1940-07-28T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1940-07-28T13:00:00-05:00" n="314"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d314">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">710.Consultation(2)/454: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the American Delegate</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hull</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1940-07-28T14:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 28, 1940—2 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>42. Your 18, July 27, 2 p.m. My heartiest and most sincere congratulations to
                    you. I fully appreciate the difficulties you have had to face and I consider
                    your success an outstanding achievement of the utmost importance to this country
                    at the present time.</p>
                <p>The press which in general was pessimistic and skeptical yesterday, is
                    exceedingly favorable once more today, and I think that when the details are
                    made public, there will be an expression of tremendous gratification on the part
                    of public opinion here.</p>
                <p>The President asked me last night to tell you how tremendously pleased he was
                    with the successful conclusion of your conferences.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
